description: Aspose.Cells for C++ is a native C++ library that offers a set of high-level APIs for most commonly used spreadsheet formats such as XLS, XLSX, XLSM and XLSB. Aspose.Cells for C++ allows you to build high performance C++ applications having the capabilities to create, manipulate and convert Excel spreadsheetswithout relying on Office Automation or Microsoft Excel application.
summary: Aspose.Cells for C++ is a native C++ library that enables the developers to add Cells handling capabilities to their C++ applications.
title: Aspose.Cells for C++
